<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir tun <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> ze <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir
                                <expan>lantman<ex>n</ex>s</expan>weise
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz der <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        durlewchtigst fürst und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Sig<ex>mund</ex></expan>, <expan>römisch<ex>er</ex></expan> und zu
                                <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc. künig, unser
                                <expan>gnedigst<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, in einer kürcz zu ewch gen Speyr komen sulle.
                                <expan>Bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                            <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>g<ex>anczem</ex></expan>
                        fleisz, wer, ob ir davon iht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> hett oder sust
                        iht <expan>fremd<ex>er</ex></expan> lewff <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> mer
                        west, die ewch füklich sein, uns zu <expan>verschr<ex>eiben,</ex></expan>
                        daz ir <add>uns</add> das bey disem <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet. Und ob ir hienach von des
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedigst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des <expan>r<ex>ömischen</ex></expan>
<expan>k<ex>ünigs</ex></expan> zukunft oder <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lewff<ex>en</ex></expan> iht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemt</expan>, daz ir
                        uns des bey <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet, sovil ewch des auch füklich
                        sey, so <expan>welln</expan> wir das pottenlon <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        beczaln, und uns in den <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewr
                                <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> und guten
                                <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> beweiset, als wir ein
                                <expan>sund<ex>er</ex></expan> gut getrawn zu ewch
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n.</expan> Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>. </ab>
